# PT Studio 7 Public API Docs

This site exposes lightweight machine-readable endpoints for automated discovery.

## Endpoints

- `GET /.well-known/api-catalog`
  - Returns RFC 9727 API catalog in RFC 9264 linkset format.
- `GET /.well-known/openapi.json`
  - OpenAPI 3.1 specification for discovery endpoints.
- `GET /.well-known/api-status`
  - Basic service health and metadata.

## Authentication

Discovery endpoints are public and do not require authentication.
